{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be playful and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EcoChic Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4169e1; /* Royal Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #a0c4ff; /* Light Blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Alice Blue */\n            --footer-color: #87ceeb; /* Sky Blue */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #a0c4ff 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000000;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(65, 105, 225, 0.7), rgba(160, 196, 255, 0.5)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/4169e1/ffffff?text=Sustainable+Fashion') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000000;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000000;\n        }\n\n        #showcase {\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        #showcase div {\n            width: 30%;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            margin: 15px;\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #showcase div:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        #showcase h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #about h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #about p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>EcoChic Threads</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Style That Cares</h2>\n            <p>Fashion-forward clothing made with love for the planet.</p>\n            <a href=\"#showcase\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Collections</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"showcase\" class=\"container\">\n        <div>\n            <h3>Organic Cotton Tees</h3>\n            <p>Soft, breathable, and kind to your skin and the earth.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150/a0c4ff/ffffff?text=Tees\" alt=\"Organic Cotton T-shirt\">\n        </div>\n        <div>\n            <h3>Recycled Denim</h3>\n            <p>Giving old jeans a stylish new life.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150/4169e1/ffffff?text=Denim\" alt=\"Recycled Denim Jeans\">\n        </div>\n        <div>\n            <h3>Linen Dresses</h3>\n            <p>Lightweight and sustainable for sunny days.</p>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150/a0c4ff/ffffff?text=Dresses\" alt=\"Linen Dress\">\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Story</h2>\n        <p>At EcoChic Threads, we believe that looking good shouldn't cost the earth. We are passionate about creating beautiful, high-quality clothing using sustainable materials and ethical practices. Join us in making a positive impact, one outfit at a time!</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More About Our Mission</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 EcoChic Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}